---

<Layout
  title="Hardwood vs Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) in Houston: Which Is Right for Your Home? | Jamail Hardwoods"
  description="Hardwood vs LVP comparison for Houston homes — cost, durability, resale value, water resistance, and which makes sense for your specific situation."
>
